Invocation Name: bar sounds
des: Immerse yourself in the cozy ambiance of a traditional bar, complete with the comforting hum of conversations, laughter, and the gentle clinking of glasses. Whether you're looking to unwind after a long day or set the mood for a friendly gathering, the Bar Sounds transports you to the heart of your favorite bar. Elevate your surroundings and evoke the spirit of camaraderie with the authentic sounds that make bar outings so special.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
